            The client will host routing, layout, auth state, and user-facing workflows across modules.
        </p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Next milestone</h2>
        <p>
            Wire the hosted application flow more tightly and prepare the first authentication screens.
        </p>
    </article>
</section>
